data.title: Lucille Ball at Freddie Prinze funeral
data.meta_description: Title supplied by cataloger.Lucille Ball arrives at Old North Church at Forest Lawn, Hollywood Hills for Freddie Prinze funeral services, with several other people. Prinze died on January 29, 1977.
